{"tid":1463843,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（突發）機場打死左兩個公安！","createTime":"2019-08-13T13:53:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T14:01:40.000Z","uid":284266,"like":7,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6c07fc7d918235d071763f14b87841ac72900cf4","tid":1463843,"uid":284266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:53:29.000Z","msg":"係呀！個標題係假架！ <br />\n<br />\n你班撚樣，而家係度捉鬼，圍公安，係咪就係你地既目的？我地個5大訴求呢？女義士隻眼呢？死左個幾位義士呢？仲有係北區醫院，文錦渡個班出唔到聲既義士呢？<br />\n<br />\n今日阻旅客走我唔會割<br />\n和理非企係度on9我唔割<br />\n入去湊熱鬧快閃我唔割<br />\n但你地而家走撚晒去圍公安，捉到鬼好撚叻？係咪之後日日捉鬼？捉到兩隻狗又好開心？之後呢？捉捉下捉到無人出黎？<br />\n<br />\n要屌就屌我，我淨係知狗屋班冷氣狗等緊我地自己散左場運動，我淨係知7婆到今日都無理我地香港人！大家集中返訴求，話返俾外國既遊客知我地既訴求。阻離境既，教埋旅客拼大使館幫手！<br />\n<br />\n屌爆我啦，但求有一兩位手足睇到！"},{"pid":"ce5de7de295fd062c5c50dc73c8951992665ad1a","tid":1463843,"uid":284266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:53:39.000Z","msg":"推你老母"},{"pid":"82c4600e39f0e4bb0f6005bfe49b010170115994","tid":1463843,"uid":280349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:55:30.000Z","msg":"放燃燒彈燒傷警察，應唔應該自首？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dDvLuS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dDvLuS</a>"},{"pid":"654ada400f532967da3c27c282cbf3eaad3dff61","tid":1463843,"uid":284266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:57:23.000Z","msg":"推呀，上熱門啦"},{"pid":"7954c5d320ecca61d8b86248fb4ae3373829a4d4","tid":1463843,"uid":229920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:57:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"984edf7e565d9c8d8ddfe680f03c8eeeac6872a5","tid":1463843,"uid":284266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:59:38.000Z","msg":"幫手叫醒返班手足呀！求下你地"},{"pid":"63ce48df8acb17d7a89365e68db7baab8fdcb2ee","tid":1463843,"uid":284266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201